Version 0.1.3 (2026-06-19)
* Configuration system: layered config from /etc/lfspkg.conf and
  ~/.config/lfspkg/lfspkg.conf with KEY=VALUE format.  Supports
  DB_ROOT and TARGET_ROOT.  LFSPKG_DB / LFSPKG_ROOT environment
  variables take highest priority.

Version 0.1.2 (2026-06-19)
* All C++ sources reformatted with clang-format GNU style.
* Added .clang-format configuration file (BasedOnStyle: GNU,
  PointerAlignment: Right).
* Added *.a to .gitignore to exclude build artifacts.

Version 0.1.1 (2026-06-19)
* Build as static library (liblfspkg.a) for linking by qp and other tools.
* built_deps: PackageMeta now records each dependency's version at build
  time, enabling detection of stale packages after dependency upgrades.
* find_stale_packages(): New public function to find packages whose
  dependencies have changed version since they were built.

Version 0.1.0 (2026-05-29)
* Autotools build system replacing hand-written Makefile.
* Modular source layout: library (db, package, util, elf) separate from CLI.
* Public C++ library API (namespace lfspkg) for use by qp and other tools.
* gettext internationalization with Chinese (zh_CN) translation.
* --help and --version flags.
End of Alpha
* Initial release: single-file package tracker with install, upgrade,
  remove, list, info, tree, owners, verify, suggest-deps commands.
